		<div id="contentLeft560">
			<h1 style="padding-top:20px;">
			Say Yes!</h1>
			<a name="sponsorForm">&nbsp;</a>
			
			<p>As parents around the world are sending their children back to school, buying new pencils and lunchboxes and backpacks, there are thousands of families in Haiti that are praying for their children to be able to go to school, but cannot afford the $35/month it takes to provide a Christ-centered education and a nutritious daily meal for them.</p>

<p>This year, God has brought 2500 new children to the Schools of Hope who desperately want to go to school and become a part of transforming their nation, but have no way of making that happen on their own. At Mission of Hope, we believe God called us to say “YES!” to these children, even though we knew it would take a God-sized miracle to find sponsors for all of them by the time school starts in September. Will you help us change a child’s life TODAY?</p>

<p>TODAY we need your help! We need YOU so that we can say yes to 2500 new students! If you have never sponsored a child, this is the time to be a part of what God is doing to change a nation, one child at a time. If each of us would say “YES!” to just one child, every one of these families who has said they want life change for their son or daughter would be able to see that happen this year. Please join me in saying “YES!” today!</p>
<p>	<em>Brad Johnson, President<br />Mission of Hope, Haiti</em></p>		
