				<form>
					<p style="padding-top:30px;">Thank you for wanting to help change the life of one student through sponsorship. Fill out the short form below to submit your commitment to a sponsorship. Upon submission our child sponsorship team will be in touch with you! 
						</p>
						<p style="padding-bottom: 0; margin-bottom: -12px; font-weight: bold;">My preference for a student is:</p>
